name: Solar System Project (Bio-Lobo)
description:
This is my Solar System Project. I have added the following elements: 

  1.  Mars
  2. Jupiter
  3. Saturn
  4. Uranus 
  5. Neptune
  6.  Pluto.

Each planet will have it's own distinct orbiting speed. A Comet spawner has been placed to show Comets .
